Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:01.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,昨天家里蒸的肉包非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我要向…高木同学告白？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:10.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然后  包子是下个月要结婚的亲戚送的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:12.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不不  不会不会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为  我又不是喜欢她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:17.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但会不会只是我没有自觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:18.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不过除了肉包  还有很多种类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:19.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,在其他人看来…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}比如豆沙包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:22.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  你觉得咖喱包怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:25.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我喜欢高木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:26.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:28.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:30.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:34.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:35.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你以前说过你喜欢披萨包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:40.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我以为你也会喜欢咖喱包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说的是咖喱包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:44.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我喜欢咖喱包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯？你以为说的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:49.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我很好奇呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你刚才好像一直在发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:55.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是一直在想那件事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:56.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就算我撒谎也会被她看穿而处在下风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这里要保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你刚才说完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是不喜欢的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你连是什么都不知道  问来有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:17.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:21.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,应该没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果一定要选  是喜欢还是讨厌？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一定要选的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,应该是不讨厌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来是喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到底是什么东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我暴露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:47.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然高木同学会捉弄我这一点很让我头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但我不讨厌和她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且觉得她挺可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  这不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:00.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我对高木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:12.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看你刚才一直满脸通红的  觉得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然不是那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,白色情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然我是有回礼的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没想到要到告白这一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:35.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完全没心思做作业
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,全怪高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这事还是应该怪滨口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:41.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,事情变成这样  果然还是高木同学的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:46.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的滨口和高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我要振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为了保持我自己的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要做的事才不是告白什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:56.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没错  战胜高木同学  仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:00.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,白色情人节是我发起进攻的绝佳节日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一定要赢给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.74,Takagi san—Picture 12-1,,0,0,0,,{\fscx161\fscy176\pos(1496,632)}自习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:12.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:13.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有点事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,新的惊吓盒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是盒子  但又不是惊吓盒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:21.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:24.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,从某种意义上说  确实会让人吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:32.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,其实我正在准备着我有史以来最大的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:33.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我把它命名为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,「西片探索」！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:40.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,3月14日  高木同学来上学的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她如果觉得会「哇！是白色情人节！」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:44.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:47.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,打开盒子以后  里面会有猜谜的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,解开之后  会被引导至下一个藏盒子的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:53.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,面对这么多难题  高木同学肯定会举手投降的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看来是我赢了  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:04.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然我不清楚情况  但你看起来很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:05.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:09.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你就等着吧  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,话说  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:16.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,3月14日那天  有件事情想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,3月14日的委托？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:24.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想  西片的话能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道说  是想拜托我向她告白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不能直接回答「嗯  好的」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,拒绝的话也感觉不太礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:37.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:40.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,在那前一天有亲戚的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:43.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到时候要坐14日早上的第一班渡轮回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我可能在第二节课的时候才能到学校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以给我抄一下第一节课的笔记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么呀  原来是这事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  我之前和你说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,三月的时候有亲戚要结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:57.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:01.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  你以为我想拜托你什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,呃  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:11.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  高木同学晚到得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有足够时间去设置「西片探索」了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,等着瞧吧  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,3月14日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这一天终于到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,赶紧开始设置「西片探索」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,首先是第一个盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,放…放不进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说起来  高木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我买了新的体育馆用鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她这样说过来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就算这样  有必要连着鞋盒一起塞进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:51.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好吧  改放她桌子里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她这是看穿了我打算设计她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不愧是高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不过  因为这点小事就放弃的话就不像我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:04.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我看看  藏第二个盒子的地方是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:12.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,终于到今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那个  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,彼此都加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是  滨口…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:24.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果为这点事就动摇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,「西片探索」就会以失败告终
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我要忘掉告白的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:37.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,春之海  终日摇荡着  摇荡着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}同学们知道这里指的是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下面只要等高木同学来上课就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是的  就是春之海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:51.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对了  说好了第一节课的笔记要借她抄来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:55.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,两组对角分别相等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以 角A等于角C
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,角B等于角D…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学怎么没来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:11.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  午休时间的图书委员就麻烦你一个人值班了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.99,Takagi san—Picture 12-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1430,610)}渡轮因为强风取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.99,Takagi san—Picture 12-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1332,676)}我明天回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:38.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还有余地  还有余地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:37.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}还有余地  还有余地…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:39.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这招如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看起来不像是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谁会这题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:55.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那么  鹰川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:57.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么嘛  高木同学今天请假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:59.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我一个月前开始学英语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:01.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不过  白色情人节的告白任务也不用做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:05.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且最重要的是  不用担心被高木同学捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能集中精力听课了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:25.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不知不觉间  我往旁边看成习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:29.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学不在的话  总觉得起不起劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:43.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,打开这个盒子的人将永远徘徊在谜题的迷宫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:46.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,想逃出去的话就接受吾辈的挑战吧  是这么写的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:48.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谜题？  挑战？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这是什么  是谁搞的恶作剧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,里面还有一张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:54.09,Takagi san—Picture 12-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(362,278)}任务一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:54.46,Takagi san—Picture 12-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(404,268)}任务一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:55.09,Takagi san—Picture 12-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(346,314)}任务一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:55.34,Takagi san—Picture 12-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(384,290)}任务一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:55.46,Takagi san—Picture 12-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(402,282)}任务一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:55.84,Takagi san—Picture 12-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,320)}任务一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:55.96,Takagi san—Picture 12-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(388,288)}任务一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:56.17,Takagi san—Picture 12-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(332,320)}任务一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:55.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,把「せ」和「ん」去掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:09.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,ti yu cang ku  体育仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道说我是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:12.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好厉害  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,体育仓库里有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:16.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,在哪里  在哪里  在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再怎么找也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:25.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:26.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.79,Takagi san—Picture 12-4,,0,0,0,,{\frx6\fry8\frz356.5\pos(640,932)\fad(150,0)}提示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:37.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,越来越有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,友加里  早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:41.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,齐心协力解开谜题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:45.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我可真是个闲人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是太遗憾了  高木同学竟然请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明明你都准备去告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就算她不请假  我也没那个打算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你就是来说这个的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  我来还书的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是上次高木同学看的书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:23.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,讲的是男子汉们不断战斗的超燃故事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:24.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:26.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,诶  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,「听八乙女如是说道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,田中的果汁掉落在地…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:35.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是这样的故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片肯定也会喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,读读看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:44.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学说不推荐我看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:45.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,把这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样放的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,理科教室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:53.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,两支铅笔的提示原来是这样用的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,第三个盒子在…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到底要玩到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:59.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我看看  是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:01.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.76,Takagi san—Picture 12-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(306,334)}任务③
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.76,Takagi san—Picture 12-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594,490)\frz356.7}酒精灯的结尾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.76,Takagi san—Picture 12-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(622,670)\frz358.6}烧杯的底部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.76,Takagi san—Picture 12-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(648,894)\frz357.8}放大镜的头部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,又是烧脑的提示
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,先准备这3样东西吧  我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:10.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没这个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,「酒精灯的结尾」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:19.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也就是最后一个字「プ」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,「烧杯的底部」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,最后的也就是长音「ー」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:25.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然后「放大镜的头部」是「ル」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:27.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,p…o o…l
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:30.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,友加里也是天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,自己的灵光一现真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好的  直接去泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:38.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:42.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,白色情人节巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,欸  挺别致的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然我喜欢吃原味的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,算了  姑且收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:52.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我往这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:08.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,北条
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:10.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:24.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:29.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:32.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我真是个窝囊废
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  你要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:58.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好像有什么消息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:02.29,Takagi san—Picture 12-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(582,444)}渡轮好像能开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:02.29,Takagi san—Picture 12-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(678,766)}也许能坐下午的航班回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.22,Takagi san—Picture 12-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1434,538)}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.22,Takagi san—Picture 12-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(902,786)}那明天学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:08.22,Takagi san—Picture 12-5,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\pos(516,722)\}已读
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:26.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,八乙女对田中说的「我喜欢你」在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但好像没有八乙女的台词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:33.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,找到田中弄掉果汁的部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:38.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:40.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果…如果那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是高木同学的恶作剧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:57.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那时候也是  那时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:01.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果都是高木同学的真心话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:10.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,稍微出个门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,终于找到第10个了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:37.26,Takagi san—Picture 12-3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz17.25\move(1328,486,1344,490,0,4444)}西片任务结束！
