Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:47.22,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}幸せに思う巡り合えたこと  オレの笑顔取り戻せたこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:51.72,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}「ありがとう」 あふれる気持ち抱き 進む道程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:56.98,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}花びらのように散り行く中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:23:02.48,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}夢みたいに 君に出逢えたキセキ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:05.19,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}愛し合って ケンカして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:08.11,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}色んな壁 二人で乗り越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:12.66,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}生まれ変わっても あなたに逢いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:17.83,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}花びらのように散ってゆく事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:23.38,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}この世界で全て受け入れてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:26.21,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}君が僕に残したモノ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.97,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}「今」という現実の宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:36.10,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}だから僕は精一杯生きて 花になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:51.37,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}如同花瓣散落一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:57.04,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}与你邂逅的奇迹如梦似幻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:21:59.83,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}相亲相爱  时而争执
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:02.75,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}两个人齐心跨越种种屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:10.89,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}即使来世  也要在你身旁化作鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:15.60,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}能一直存在下去吗  在我头顶高照的艳阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:21.23,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}能一直守护到底吗  你喜怒哀乐的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:23.78,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}若终有一日消失荡然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:26.40,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那就更多地感激两人的邂逅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:29.11,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那一天  那一刻  那一处的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:31.66,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}又将创造全新的轨迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:36.96,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}因为有爱从而变得坚强  因为信任从而突破难关
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.88,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你留下的东西依旧在我心中闪耀发光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:47.22,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}无论是我们幸福的邂逅  还是我被重拾的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:51.72,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}胸中满怀感激之情  迈向前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:56.98,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}如同花瓣散落一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:23:02.48,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}与你邂逅的奇迹如梦似幻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:05.19,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}相亲相爱  时而争执
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:08.11,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}两个人齐心跨越种种屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:12.66,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}即使来世也想与你相会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:17.83,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}如同花瓣散落一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:23.38,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}去接受这个世间的千千万万
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:26.21,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你给我留下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.97,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是名为「当下」真实的宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:36.10,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}于是我拼尽全力生活  化作鲜花
